<para>The <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Magnifier</application>
package contains
<command>magnifier</command> and
<filename class="libraryfile">libgnome-mag</filename>.
</para>

</sect2>

<sect2><title>Description</title>

<sect3><title>magnifier</title>
